    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited to show you my pride and joy. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and truly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and has been treated with so much love. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. If you want a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Come say hi and take it for a spin! \u2728",
