    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-revving valvetrain. This example boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been comprehensively serviced, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure peak structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut, riding on original staggered Style 67 alloys. Finished in a concours-ready Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this specimen exhibits zero paint meter deviations and a pristine undercarriage. A true purist\u2019s machine with linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback.",
